      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and factory limited-slip differential for an engaging, analog driving experience. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to ensure optimal timing and structural rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and communicative steering rack, while the engine pulls strong to its 8,000 RPM redline. Expect a well-sorted driver's car with minor cosmetic patina that reflects its authentic road use.",
