      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful daily use such as faint road peppering on the hood. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine environment; the leather seating is supple and free of cracks, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All onboard technology, including the navigation and premium audio system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car is mechanically robust, featuring a complete service log, a recently replaced battery, and tires with deep tread remaining. The engine idles quietly and pulls smoothly, reflecting a life of consistent, preventative maintenance. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept vehicle that delivers a 'like-new' driving experience without the 'new' price tag.",
